Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: The Happy Virus
Description: February 28
---
I caught the happy virus again last night when I was out singing
beneath the stars. It is remarkably contagious, so kiss me!
